      "apiVersion": "2017-07-01",
      "name": "[parameters('workflows_mackerel_alert_counter_name')]",
      "location": "japaneast",
      "dependsOn": [
        "[resourceId('Microsoft.Web/connections', parameters('connections_mackerel_api_name'))]",
        "[resourceId('Microsoft.Web/customApis', parameters('customApis_mackerel_api_name'))]"
      ],
      "properties": {
        "state": "Disabled",
        "definition": {
          "$schema": "https://schema.management.azure.com/providers/Microsoft.Logic/schemas/2016-06-01/workflowdefinition.json#",
          "contentVersion": "1.0.0.0",
          "parameters": {
            "$connections": {
              "defaultValue": {},
              "type": "Object"
            }
          },
          "triggers": {
            "Recurrence": {
              "recurrence": {
                "frequency": "Minute",
                "interval": 30
              },
              "type": "Recurrence"
            }
          },
          "actions": {
            "getAlerts": {
              "runAfter": {},
              "type": "ApiConnection",
              "inputs": {
                "host": {
                  "connection": {
                    "name": "@parameters('$connections')['mackerel-api']['connectionId']"
                  }
                },
                "method": "get",
                "path": "/alerts"
              }
            },
            "postServiceMetric": {
              "runAfter": {
                "getAlerts": [
                  "Succeeded"
                ]
              },
              "type": "ApiConnection",
              "inputs": {
                "body": [
                  {
                    "name": "alerts.open",
                    "time": "@div(ticks(subtractFromTime(utcNow(), 1969, 'Year')), 10000000)",
                    "value": "@length(body('getAlerts')?['alerts'])"
                  }
                ],
                "host": {
                  "connection": {
                    "name": "@parameters('$connections')['mackerel-api']['connectionId']"
                  }
                },
                "method": "post",
                "path": "/services/@{encodeURIComponent('sandbox')}/tsdb"
              }
            }
          },
          "outputs": {}
        },
        "parameters": {
          "$connections": {
            "value": {
              "mackerel-api": {
                "connectionId": "[resourceId('Microsoft.Web/connections', parameters('connections_mackerel_api_name'))]",
                "connectionName": "mackerel-api",
                "id": "[resourceId('Microsoft.Web/customApis', parameters('customApis_mackerel_api_name'))]"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
